# AI Gateway — Project Overview

## What This Project Is

A **production-grade AI Gateway** — a provider-agnostic HTTP API that routes AI workloads (chat, embeddings, vision, agents, RAG) to multiple LLM backends.

## What This Project Is NOT

- Not a chatbot UI
- Not a coding assistant or IDE plugin
- Not tied to a single LLM vendor

## Current Status (v0.1.0)

| Phase | Status |
|-------|--------|
| 1 — Project Foundation | Complete |
| 2 — AI Gateway Core | Complete |
| 3 — Persistence Layer | In progress (3.1–3.2.1 complete) |

**Live endpoints:** `GET /`, `GET /health`, `POST /chat`

**Default provider:** Ollama (`qwen3:8b`)

## Repository Layout

```
backend/src/
  api/          # Routes + FastAPI dependencies
  core/         # Config, DB engine, logging, lifespan, exceptions
  middleware/   # Request ID, response timing
  models/       # SQLAlchemy ORM base + mixins
  schemas/      # Pydantic request/response DTOs
  services/     # Business logic + LLM provider implementations
docs/           # Canonical project documentation
```

